data.description: Nestled in a private, gated community with a stunning golf course as your backyard, you will discover your dream home here.  This spacious 5-bdrm, 3-ba home is designed for comfort and style; offering something special for every member of your family. Come inside and feel the elegance of tile floors and newly-installed carpet. Cook gourmet meals in a modern kitchen featuring gorgeous granite counters and a stylish subway tile backsplash. This home features a separate living room and family room for even more space to relax and enjoy. Looking for stunning views, the balcony off the main bedroom offers amazing vistas of the city and mountains, making it your perfect morning coffee spot. In addition, the home has many energy saving features including solar panels which are owned, not leased!
